ksdk:manifest.name: SDK version 2.4.1 package for FRDM-KL27Z board
ksdk:manifest.brief: This is SDK version 2.4.1 manifest file. It describes the content of the SDK version 2.4.1 package for FRDM-KL27Z board and additional settings for tools that support SDK version 2.4.1

board.name: FRDM-KL27Z
board.description: FRDM-KL27Z: Freedom Development Platform for Kinetis KL17 and KL27 MCUs

specific.content:
The FRDM-KL27Z is an ultra-low-cost development platform for the Kinetis速 L Series KL17 and KL27 MCUs built on the ARM速 Cortex速-M0+ processor.
  • Features include easy access to MCU I/O, battery-ready, low-power operation, a standard-based form factor with expansion board options and a built-in debug interface for flash programming and run-control
  • The FRDM-KL27Z is supported by a range of NXP速 and third-party development software.

device.name: MKL27Z644
device.description: KL2x: Kinetis速 KL2x-48 MHz, USB Ultra-Low-Power Microcontrollers (MCUs) based on ARM速 Cortex速-M0+ Core

specific.content:
The Kinetis速 KL2x is an ultra-low-power MCU family that adds a full-speed USB 2.0 On-the-Go (OTG) controller or a full-speed crystal-less USB 2.0 device controller in addition to the Kinetis KL1x series.
The Kinetis KL2x MCU family is compatible with Kinetis K20 MCUs (based on ARM速 Cortex速-M4), and with all other Kinetis KL1x, KL2x, KL3x, and KL4x series MCUs, providing a migration path to lower and higher performance and feature integration.
